    "description": "Nippon Pigment Holdings Company Limited manufactures and sells liquid dispersion products, colorants, and resin compounds in Japan and internationally. The company offers various resin compounds, such as olefin and styrene resins, and engineering plastic products; resin colorants for automobile interior and exterior parts, as well as plastic containers, such as shampoo, films, sheets, and fibers; and colorants for automotive interior coverings, sealing materials, flooring materials, etc. It also provides liquid dispersions for FPD colour filters, etc.; and other resin colorants. The company was formerly known as Nippon Pigment Company Limited and changed its name to Nippon Pigment Holdings Company Limited in October 2024. The company was founded in 1925 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
